            <title>[HADOOP-17496] Build failure due to python2.7 deprecation by pip</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HADOOP-17496</link>
                <project id="12310240" key="HADOOP">Hadoop Common</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The latest version of pip has deprecated its support for python 2.7 -&#160;&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/pypa/pip/issues/9500&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;pip install on Python 2 fails with SyntaxError: sys.stderr.write(f&quot;ERROR: {exc}&quot;) &#183; Issue #9500 &#183; pypa/pip (github.com)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We encounter the following error while building Hadoop -&lt;/p&gt;
